1
00:00:30,474 --> 00:00:39,500
Hello, I'm Richard Katz, and I'll be speaking today about the character pipeline I worked on at Zenimax Online Studios for The Elder Scrolls Online.

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:53,028
